Combine the olive oil, red wine vinegar and balsamic vinegar in a bowl and whisk until emulsified. Add the salt and pepper and whisk to mix well. Arrange the tomatoes in a 9Ã—13-inch dish. Sprinkle with the garlic and basil. Pour the vinegar mixture evenly over the top. Marinate in the refrigerator for 12 hours. Top with asiago cheese.